'''神學碩士'''（Master of Theology）是在[[大學|大學]]或基督教[[神學院|神學院]]針對進階神學研究所設立的[[學位|學位]]<ref name="autogenerated1">{{citation|url=http://www.ats.edu/MemberSchools/Pages/Degrees.aspx|title=ATS - Approved Degrees|publisher=Association of Theological Schools in the United States and Canada|accessdate=2012-12-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130406092527/http://www.ats.edu/MemberSchools/Pages/Degrees.aspx|archivedate=2013-04-06|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

==北美==
若要在{{le|北美聯合神學教育院校協會|Association of Theological Schools}}所認證的學院教授神學相關課程，至少要有神學碩士的學歷。神學碩士一般要先取得{{le|道學碩士|Master of Divinity}}（M.Div.）或是其他三年的研究所神學課程後，才能進修神學碩士課程。神學碩士一般會有一年至二年有關特定神學主題的進行研究，可能需要綜合性的學科考試及研究論文，也可能不需要。一般神學碩士是強調學術研究的進階研究學位，也是在取得{{le|道學碩士|Master of Divinity}}（M.Div.）後的第二個神學相關學位<ref name="autogenerated1"/><ref>See {{citation|url=http://www.asburyseminary.edu/admissions/apply/apply-advanced-research-programs/|title=Advanced Research Programs (Th.M., Ph.D.)|publisher=Asbury Theological Seminary|accessdate=2012-12-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113213722/http://www.asburyseminary.edu/admissions/apply/apply-advanced-research-programs/|archivedate=2012-11-13}} and {{citation|url=http://divinity.duke.edu/academics/degrees/master-theology|title=Master of Theology (Th.M.)|publisher=[[Duke_University|Duke University]]|accessdate=2012-12-08|archive-date=2016-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201143938/https://divinity.duke.edu/academics/degrees/master-theology|dead-url=no}} for examples.</ref>。

